ia.placeholder.com/100/ff7043/000000?text=P4\" alt=\"Podcast 4 Icon\">\n                <h3>Global Echoes</h3>\n                <p>Understand the world with insightful conversations on international affairs and culture.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"listen-button\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Podwave Network</h2>\n            <p>Podwave Network is dedicated to bringing you high-quality audio content across a diverse range of genres. We partner with passionate creators to deliver engaging podcasts that inform, entertain, and inspire. Join us on a journey through sound.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have a podcast you'd like to feature or a question for us?</p>\n        <p>Email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@podwave.net\">info@podwave.net</a></p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Podwave Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}